  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "第一章 父亲的三件赏赐",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "27689985_6_15708-15730",
          "range": "15708-15730",
          "rangeStart": 15708,
          "rangeEnd": 15730,
          "markText": "对过去不后悔，对现在有信心，对未来满是希望。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1727310235,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-09-26 08:23:55",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15708&rangeEnd=15730",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15708&rangeEnd=15730"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_6_15708-15730",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "15708-15730",
      "markText": "对过去不后悔，对现在有信心，对未来满是希望。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15708&rangeEnd=15730",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15708&rangeEnd=15730"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_3_542-561",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "542-561",
      "markText": "历史是什么？不过是我用来挂小说的钉子。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=542&rangeEnd=561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=542&rangeEnd=561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_26_3985-4032",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "3985-4032",
      "markText": "一个民族的命运和许多人的性命，有时候竟挂在何等脆弱而且不可知的线索上面，这使得达达尼昂惊叹了。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=3985&rangeEnd=4032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=3985&rangeEnd=4032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_6_2984-3010",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2984-3010",
      "markText": "你遇到任何事都要争上风，并且活得快快乐乐，长命百岁。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2984&rangeEnd=3010",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2984&rangeEnd=3010"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_31_561-602",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "561-602",
      "markText": "因为他深信若要和一个人维持交谊，决不可揭穿他的秘密，尤其是那种和自尊心有关的秘密。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=561&rangeEnd=602",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=561&rangeEnd=602"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_6_1900-1922",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1900-1922",
      "markText": "人们因为轻视这匹马，同时也轻视起骑马的人来。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1900&rangeEnd=1922",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1900&rangeEnd=1922"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_13_1217-1247",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1217-1247",
      "markText": "他带了他的队伍到神甫家里去，他们吃光了神甫准备吃两个月的饮食",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1217&rangeEnd=1247",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1217&rangeEnd=1247"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_6_15152-15197",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "15152-15197",
      "markText": "他把黄马卖了三个埃居，这价钱是卖得还不算坏，因为达达尼昂在最后那段行程里教它跑的路太多了。",
      "totalCount": 66,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15152&rangeEnd=15197",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15152&rangeEnd=15197"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_39_940-1003",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "940-1003",
      "markText": "“就常情来说，”他说，“向人请教的人不过是为了不听从劝告。或者倘若听从劝告，不过是为了事后可以抱怨某一个人不应该给他出主意。”",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=940&rangeEnd=1003",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=940&rangeEnd=1003"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_9_8412-8506",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "8412-8506",
      "markText": "两个青年互相敬礼后，阿拉密斯从那条通往卢森堡宫的街道往上走，达达尼昂则向着圣衣会走去。他一面走，一面暗自说：“千真万确，我是回不来的了。不过，如果我被人杀死，那至少是被一个火枪手杀死的。”",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8412&rangeEnd=8506",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=8412&rangeEnd=8506"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_12_486-530",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "486-530",
      "markText": "阿多斯劝他到松果园好好吃一顿，波尔多斯劝他雇用一个跟班，阿拉密斯则劝他找一个称心的情妇。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27689985&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=486&rangeEnd=530",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a1632e0071a68401a168bc1?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=486&rangeEnd=530"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27689985_16_1222-1299",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1222-1299",
      "markText": "富有的女人除美貌以外，还布施她们一部分的钱财。可以说，那个风流时代的许多英雄，当初如果没有情妇把相当充实的钱包系在他的鞍轿上，是不能立功于前和成名于后的。",
